HTZSafe offers voice-controlled smarthome experience with Alexa. Control your HTZSafe security panel hands free.
Just say it, HTZSafe will obey.

Here's a step by step guide:
1) Visit https://h5.htziot.com and register, you can reigster by email or mobile phone number;
2) Login to your profile, add your device(s);
3) Lauch Alexa app and search 'HTZSafe' in 'Skills and Games';
4) Go thourgh acount linking steps and return to Alexa APP;
5) You will see your device(s) in Alexa APP's 'Devices';
6) Congrats, now you can say: 'Alexa, arm my [your-device-name]' to controll it!

Here are the voice commands HTZSafe has:

ARM
Alexa, arm my [your-device-name].

DISARM
Alexa, disarm my [your-device-name].

REPORT STATE
Alexa, is my [your-device-name] armed?
